<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes rather than fire primarily disturb the alliance. <i>Scirpus microcarpus </i>can sprout after a fire.</div>
